creator: Wildflower Cases
descriptionHtml: Founded in 2012, Wildflower Cases is a female-owned and operated iPhone accessory company. Each exclusive and limited edition fashion iPhone accessory is designed by founder Michelle Carlson and her two daughters, Devon Lee and Sydney Carlson. The family’s passion of customizing cases quickly transformed into a thriving business following a chance encounter with Miley Cyrus. Cyrus spotted the sisters’ cases at a restaurant and encouraged them to sell their designs online as a brand. The popstar went on to tweet @Wildflower Cases — and the rest was history. Shop Wildflower Cases exclusively on our app and don’t forget to tag us in your super cute pics!
